metadata.name: Rogue Dice
metadata.description: The Rogue Dice Club is a collection of 6,000 Unique Rogue Dice NFT's - Unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum Blockchain. Your Rogue will serve as your Rogue Dice Club membership card and grants you access to members-only benefits. Rogue Dice's will be playable characters in Rogue World & will all have their own unique traits and abilities.
